data.name: CONVENTIONAL ARTERIAL BLOOD SAMPLERS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)
- Gasket: Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber

## STERILIZATION
- Gamma Sterilization (R)

## PRESENTATIONS
- Luer Lock and Luer Slip Tips
- With and Without Needle
- Latex -free Gasket
- Customizable graduation including logo
- Including Needle Safe Silicon Rubber Dice
- Including Syringe Luer Cap

## PERFORMANCE
- Ultra-precision sprayed solid heparin lithium
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency Barrel
- Smooth sliding
- Smooth Surface
- Luer cap
- Silicon Rubber
